<br>
Every tom dick and harry who wouldn't bother posting a response is eager to chime in their two cents and therefore bump useless posts up to the top and force actual worthwhile content down the list.<br>
<br>
While we are at it, have you guys considered creating a low level, mid level, and high level forums? I am really digging the way those uptight pallies got their forums set up <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Would really increase the signal to noise ratio. The lack of which is making this messageboard painful to surf.<br>
<br>
Greedy reason: Painful to surf = less likely to keep developers and designers in SOE up to date with our issues! <p><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:13px"><b>Veteran
